Experience the Global Advantage


Global Financial Services, LLC is a leading wealth management firm based in Houston, Texas, that specializes in meeting the domestic and international investing needs of high-net worth individuals, families and corporations. Since 1994, Global has offered the highest levels of market experience, integrity, confidentiality and personalized service to clients. We distinguish ourselves not only by what we do, but through continuous client interaction aimed at understanding, implementing, managing and evaluating. We pride ourselves in delivering an uncommon level of individual service and client satisfaction. To schedule a free consultation, contact us.
Check the background of this firm on FINRA’s BrokerCheck.









Just as every situation is different, so is every financial plan. Let’s have a conversation about how the Global team can help you reach your financial goals.
































 




GFS Advisors LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:05 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of GFS Advisors LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
GFS Advisors LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals and corporations and other businesses. The firm manages client focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. The firm also invests in exchange traded funds. It employs fundamental and technical analysis to make its investments. The firm uses a combination of external and internal research to make its investments. It is based in Houston, Texas. GFS Advisors LLC operates as a subsidiary of The Edelman Financial Group, Inc.


1330 Post Oak BoulevardSuite 2100Houston, TX 77056United States



Phone: 713-968-0400

Fax: 713-968-0499








